---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Refund & Cancellation | Seetayya Foundation" description="Refund and cancellation information for Seetayya Foundation donations.">
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="container-pad max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-ink">Refund & Cancellation</h1>
      <div class="rich-content mt-8 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/74">
        <ol>
          <li>You will provide authentic, correct, and true information while completing the process for online donation. Seetayya Foundation reserves the right to confirm and validate the information and other details provided by you at any point of time. If, upon confirmation, your details are found not to be true wholly or partly, Seetayya Foundation has the right in its sole discretion to reject the donation.</li>
          <li>If a donor feels that he or she made an error in donation amount, purpose, or any other parameter, kindly let Seetayya Foundation know about such error within 7 working days by email to seetayyafoundation1@gmail.com. We shall rectify any such parameter requested by you whenever possible.</li>
          <li>You will receive a confirmation on successful or failed transaction.</li>
          <li>No refund or cancellation request for the donated amount by any donor will be entertained for online donations through the online payment gateway after the donation is accepted from our online payment gateway service providers, unless there is a fraud notification from our payment gateway service providers.</li>
          <li>Only Indian donors are eligible for a tax exemption certificate under section 80G of the Income Tax Act, and it would be sent to the registered address provided during the process of online donation.</li>
          <li>If the Indian donor does not receive an 80G certificate within 45 days from the time of donation, he or she is liable to claim the donated amount from Seetayya Foundation.</li>
          <li>For any other information on online donations, kindly write to seetayyafoundation1@gmail.com or call us on +91 9490596331, +91 7386374850.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
